    "action": {
      "type": "SET_CONTENT",
      "input": {
        "content": "# billing-utils computes subscription billing breakdowns and metric overages\n\nLocated at `editors/subscription-instance-editor/components/billing-utils.ts`, this module handles all billing display logic for active subscriptions.\n\n## Key Exports\n\n| Function | Purpose | Used By |\n|----------|---------|--------|\n| `formatCurrency(amount, currency)` | Intl.NumberFormat currency display | BillingPanel, ServicesPanel |\n| `formatDate(date)` | Localized date strings | BillingPanel, SubscriptionHeader |\n| `formatBillingCycleSuffix(cycle)` | Cycle suffixes (/mo, /qtr, /yr) | Various |\n| `formatDiscountBadge(discount)` | \"X% off\" or \"$X off\" display | BillingPanel |\n| `getDiscountSourceLabel(source)` | Label discount source | BillingPanel |\n| `computeMetricOverage(metric)` | Calculate usage overage costs | Internal |\n| `computeBillingBreakdown(state)` | Complete billing analysis | BillingPanel |\n\n## computeBillingBreakdown\n\nThe main function. Takes `SubscriptionInstanceState` and returns:\n- Fixed total (group recurring costs)\n- Dynamic total (metric overage projections)\n- Projected total\n- Per-group breakdowns with discount info\n- Setup cost lines with paid/unpaid status\n- Standalone service costs\n\n---\n\nTopics:\n- [[helper functions]]",
        "updatedAt": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
      },
      "timestampUtcMs": "2026-05-13T13:00:28.000Z"
    }
  },
